# ── Capacitor / Android (generated native shell) ───────────────────────────
# The android/ folder is regenerable via `npx cap add android` + `npx cap sync`,
# so we ignore it wholesale. To COMMIT the native project instead (for custom
# icons/splash/native code), comment the next line and uncomment the granular
# block below it.
/android/
# /android/.gradle/
# /android/build/
# /android/app/build/
# /android/captures/
# /android/local.properties
# /android/.idea/
# /android/app/release/

# Gradle / Android build outputs
*.apk
*.aab
local.properties

# Signing material — NEVER commit
*.keystore
*.jks
keystore.properties
